The paper focuses on facial attribute extraction using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the robustness of these networks against adversarial attacks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the concept of natural adversarial samples, which relates to computer security (cs.CR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
